    "source": "codex-fusion",
    "confidence": "high",
    "text": "\\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{1-\\alpha_{t-1}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}\n+\\frac{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t-1}}\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\mathbf{x}\n&=\n\\frac{1-\\alpha_{t-1}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}\n+\\frac{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t-1}}\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\n\\left(\n\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}\n-\\frac{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}}{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t}}}\\boldsymbol{\\epsilon}\n\\right) \\\\\n&=\n\\frac{1-\\alpha_{t-1}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}\n+\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\n\\left(\n\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}\n-\\frac{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\boldsymbol{\\epsilon}\n\\right).\n\\end{aligned} \\quad (18.32)"
