    "order": 5,
    "type": "equation",
    "source": "codex-fusion",
    "confidence": "high",
    "text": "\\begin{aligned}\nL[\\phi_{1\\ldots T}]\n&=\n\\sum_{i=1}^{I}\n\\Bigg(\n-\\log\\left[\n\\mathsf{Norm}_{\\mathbf{x}_{i}}\n\\left[\n\\mathbf{f}_{1}[\\mathbf{z}_{i1},\\phi_{1}],\\sigma_{1}^{2}\\mathbf{I}\n\\right]\n\\right] \\\\\n&\\qquad\\qquad\n+\\sum_{t=2}^{T}\n\\frac{1}{2\\sigma_{t}^{2}}\n\\left\\|\n\\left(\n\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_t}}\\mathbf{z}_{it}\n-\\frac{\\beta_t}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_t}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_t}}\\boldsymbol{\\epsilon}_{it}\n\\right)\n-\\mathbf{f}_{t}[\\mathbf{z}_{it},\\phi_{t}]\n\\right\\|^{2}\n\\Bigg).\n\\end{aligned} \\quad (18.34)"
